00:00:23.350 --> 00:00:26.854 position:5% line:77% align:start
Don't you need to tell Sanae and
your old man that you're going
to school?

00:02:05.407 --> 00:02:08.311 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa] Those pictures...
[Tomoya] Yeah?

00:02:08.411 --> 00:02:11.948 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa] My father use to
be an actor. I had no idea.

00:02:12.049 --> 00:02:15.620 position:5% line:77% align:start
He was really popular in
student theater back when
he was in high school.

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:19.826 position:5% line:83% align:start
Apparently, he won a bunch
of competitions, too.

00:02:19.926 --> 00:02:21.828 position:5% line:89% align:start
They never said a word to me.

00:02:21.929 --> 00:02:26.366 position:5% line:77% align:start
I knew my mother used to be a
middle school teacher,. but
that's all they told me.

00:02:31.606 --> 00:02:35.644 position:5% line:77% align:start
I couldn't help but notice
how happy my parents looked
in all those photos.

00:02:35.744 --> 00:02:38.515 position:5% line:77% align:start
But of course they were happy.
They were living out their
dreams.

00:02:38.615 --> 00:02:40.450 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] Nagisa...
[Nagisa] Not only that,

00:02:40.550 --> 00:02:43.955 position:5% line:83% align:start
it was a happiness that
could've lasted forever.

00:02:44.054 --> 00:02:46.324 position:5% line:89% align:start
If only I... was never born.

00:02:46.424 --> 00:02:49.896 position:5% line:77% align:start
That's not true! Besides,
don't you think they're
still happy now?

00:02:49.995 --> 00:02:52.699 position:5% line:83% align:start
But they still had to
give up on their dreams.

00:02:52.799 --> 00:02:54.133 position:5% line:89% align:start
Am I wrong?

00:02:55.970 --> 00:02:59.373 position:5% line:83% align:start
And look at me... all this time
I've been trying to live out my

00:02:59.473 --> 00:03:03.111 position:5% line:83% align:start
dream without ever thinking that
they had to sacrifice theirs.

00:03:03.211 --> 00:03:05.581 position:5% line:83% align:start
And I did the same
thing to you too.

00:03:05.681 --> 00:03:06.883 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm so ungrateful.

00:03:06.983 --> 00:03:09.385 position:5% line:83% align:start
I've been such a terrible
daughter to them.

00:03:09.485 --> 00:03:13.690 position:5% line:77% align:start
I was so set on my dream,
I've made everyone
else suffer for it.

00:03:13.791 --> 00:03:15.793 position:5% line:89% align:start
I've wasted all their time.

00:03:15.894 --> 00:03:17.963 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's not a waste.
We wanted to help.

00:03:18.062 --> 00:03:19.565 position:5% line:83% align:start
But if you get discouraged
and give up now,

00:03:19.665 --> 00:03:22.601 position:5% line:77% align:start
then all the work that
everyone's done will
be for nothing.

00:03:23.904 --> 00:03:28.041 position:5% line:83% align:start
We all gave it our best to make
it this far. We can't give up!

00:03:52.337 --> 00:03:54.006 position:5% line:89% align:start
I could really go for a nap.

00:03:54.106 --> 00:03:56.208 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're not nervous at all,
are you?

00:03:56.309 --> 00:03:59.346 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Ryou] Nagisa, what's wrong?
[Nagisa] Huh?

00:03:59.446 --> 00:04:01.983 position:5% line:83% align:start
She's just a little stressed
out about the show, that's all.

00:04:02.082 --> 00:04:04.652 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] Tell them.
[Nagisa] Uh, yeah.

00:04:04.753 --> 00:04:07.489 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Youhei] What's going on?
She's acting kind of strange.

00:04:07.590 --> 00:04:09.025 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] It's kind
of a long story.

00:04:09.124 --> 00:04:11.126 position:5% line:89% align:start
Just try to act normal, okay?

00:04:11.861 --> 00:04:13.196 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Youhei sighs]

00:04:15.533 --> 00:04:18.302 position:5% line:83% align:start
Nagisa, let me show you a
little trick for good luck.

00:04:18.402 --> 00:04:21.406 position:5% line:83% align:start
Write the character for "person"
on your hand three times.

00:04:21.506 --> 00:04:23.643 position:5% line:89% align:start
Person, person, person...

00:04:23.743 --> 00:04:26.446 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Kotomi] That's the character
for "enter," not "person."
[Youhei] Who cares?!

00:04:26.546 --> 00:04:28.782 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Youhei] Just let me finish!
[Kyou] If you can't
write the kanji,

00:04:28.882 --> 00:04:31.819 position:5% line:71% align:start
[Kyou] then the trick
isn't gonna work.
[Youhei] It's the thought
that counts, okay?!

00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:34.856 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Kyou] Oh, give me a break!
[Youhei] What does it
matter to you, anyway?!

00:04:34.956 --> 00:04:36.324 position:5% line:89% align:start
Our performance isn't til later.

00:04:36.424 --> 00:04:37.860 position:5% line:83% align:start
You wanna walk around
for a little bit?

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:40.363 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Youhei] Oh yeah, I should
probably show Mei around.

00:04:40.463 --> 00:04:44.267 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then we'll just do our own thing
until the performance, okay?

00:04:44.368 --> 00:04:45.870 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] So, what do
you wanna check out?

00:04:48.606 --> 00:04:49.641 position:5% line:89% align:start
Nagisa!

00:04:49.741 --> 00:04:51.844 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa] Oh, uh wait,
what was that?

00:04:53.912 --> 00:04:58.618 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'm sorry. I know I need to
keep it together for the
performance today...

00:04:58.718 --> 00:05:01.656 position:5% line:83% align:start
but I still have a lot
of stuff on my mind.

00:05:03.391 --> 00:05:05.661 position:5% line:83% align:start
But I took what you
said earlier to heart.

00:05:05.761 --> 00:05:08.430 position:5% line:83% align:start
The thing about us all working
on the play together, I mean.

00:05:08.530 --> 00:05:12.435 position:5% line:77% align:start
It wouldn't be fair to everyone
else if I ruined the show
just 'cause I was upset.

00:05:12.535 --> 00:05:15.973 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hpmh. That's right,
just hang in there.

00:05:16.073 --> 00:05:17.408 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] Right.

00:05:39.568 --> 00:05:41.370 position:5% line:89% align:start
